Weekly Events & Live Entertainment in the Heart of Miami
Step beneath the surface and discover a new side of Miami nightlife at 9 Feet Under Speakeasy Lounge. Join us each week for Karaoke Thursdays and Live Jazz Fridays, set against a backdrop of vintage ambiance and expertly crafted cocktails. Close out the weekend with our signature Tropical Sundays, featuring a live DJ spinning from 5PM to midnight. Timeless music, curated drinks, and the soul of Miamiâ€”every night, just below.
THURSDAYS
Karaoke 9 - Midnight
Take the stage every Thursday from 9PM-12AM at 9 Feet Under Speakeasy Lounge for a night of music, energy, and unforgettable performances. Whether you're a seasoned singer or just in it for fun, our karaoke nights are the perfect way to let loose. Enjoy handcrafted specialty cocktails while you sing your heart out in Miamiâ€™s most stylish speakeasy setting.
FRIDAYS
Live Jazz 9 - Midnight
Unwind in style every Friday from 9PM-12AM with Live Jazz Nights at 9 Feet Under Speakeasy Lounge. Let the smooth sounds of live jazz set the tone for your weekend as you sip on expertly crafted specialty cocktails. With a vintage vibe and an intimate atmosphere, our lounge offers the perfect setting to relax, connect, and experience the soulful side of Miami nightlife.

About Us - 9 Feet Under: Miami's Premier Speakeasy
Nestled in the heart of Miami at 885 Southeast 14th Street, 9 Feet Under is Miami's premier hidden speakeasy lounge that masterfully blends Prohibition-era elegance with contemporary nightlife sophistication. Our underground venue offers an intimate escape from the ordinary, where expertly crafted cocktails meet timeless ambiance in a setting that celebrates both heritage and innovation. Since opening our doors, we've become the destination of choice for discerning guests seeking elevated experiences, authentic connections, and unforgettable evenings. Step beneath the surface and discover Miami's best-kept secret, where every visit promises to transport you to a world of refined luxury and genuine hospitality.
Our Mission
At 9 Feet Under, our mission is to create exceptional experiences through expertly crafted cocktails, curated entertainment, and a timeless atmosphere that honors the golden age of speakeasies. We are dedicated to being Miami's premier destination for elevated nightlife, where professional bartenders craft signature cocktails using premium ingredients, and every guest enjoys genuine connection in an environment that celebrates both sophistication and authenticity. Our commitment extends beyond serving drinksâ€”we curate unforgettable moments that bring people together in a space where quality, craftsmanship, and community converge.
Our Vision
We envision 9 Feet Under as the definitive speakeasy experience in Miami, setting the standard for craft cocktail culture and intimate entertainment venues throughout South Florida. Our vision is to preserve and evolve the speakeasy tradition, creating a timeless sanctuary where modern Miami meets classic elegance, and where each guest becomes part of our extended family. We strive to be recognized as the premier underground venue that consistently delivers exceptional service, innovative mixology, and an atmosphere that inspires return visits and lasting memories.
